      {/* Build your scraper */}
      <h2 class='mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-white'>## Build your scraper</h2>
      <p class='mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed'>
        Tell the AI agent what data you need. It understands your intent and builds a
        scraper that extracts exactly what you're looking for, in the schema you define.
      </p>

      <pre
        class='mb-6 overflow-x-auto bg-[#151517] p-4 text-sm'>{`{
  "product_name": "string",
  "price": "number",
  "availability": "boolean",
  "features": ["string"],
  "description": "string"
}`}</pre>

      <p class='mb-16 text-base leading-relaxed'>
        The AI agent automatically navigates pages, handles pagination, and extracts data
        according to your schema. No more brittle CSS selectors or XPath queries.
      </p>

      {/* Automatically respond to changes */}
      <h2 class='mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-white'>
        ## Automatically respond to changes
      </h2>
      <p class='mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed'>
        When websites change their layout or structure, traditional scrapers break.
        Vibescraper's AI agent automatically adapts to these changes.
      </p>

      <ul class='mb-16 space-y-2 text-base'>
        <li>* Periodic QA checks ensure data quality</li>
        <li>* Monitor pages over time with version history</li>
        <li>* Edit schemas on the fly or let the AI suggest improvements</li>
        <li>* Automatic error recovery and retry logic</li>
      </ul>

      {/* Query your data */}
      <h2 class='mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-white'>## Query your data</h2>
      <p class='mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed'>
        Access your scraped data through multiple interfaces designed for different use
        cases.
      </p>

      <ul class='mb-16 space-y-2 text-base'>
        <li>* SQL analysis for complex queries</li>
        <li>* Tell the AI agent to analyze data for you</li>
        <li>* Simple JSON API for programmatic access</li>
        <li>* Export everything in standard formats</li>
      </ul>

